import React from 'react';

import Grid from '@material-ui/core/Grid';
import { withStyles } from '@material-ui/core/styles';
import Button from '@material-ui/core/Button';
import Dialog from '@material-ui/core/Dialog';
import MuiDialogTitle from '@material-ui/core/DialogTitle';
import MuiDialogContent from '@material-ui/core/DialogContent';
import MuiDialogActions from '@material-ui/core/DialogActions';
import IconButton from '@material-ui/core/IconButton';
import CloseIcon from '@material-ui/icons/Close';
import Typography from '@material-ui/core/Typography';

import { 
    HeaderProfileContainer,
    GridContainer
} from './select-elo-styles';

import Box from '@material-ui/core/Box';

const styles = (theme) => ({
root: {
    margin: 0,
    padding: theme.spacing(2),
},
closeButton: {
    position: 'absolute',
    right: theme.spacing(1),
    top: theme.spacing(1),
    color: theme.palette.grey[500],
},
});

const DialogTitle = withStyles(styles)((props) => {
    const { children, classes, onClose, ...other } = props;
    return (
        <MuiDialogTitle disableTypography className={classes.root} {...other}>
        <Typography variant="h6">{children}</Typography>
        {onClose ? (
            <IconButton aria-label="close" className={classes.closeButton} onClick={onClose}>
            <CloseIcon />
            </IconButton>
        ) : null}
        </MuiDialogTitle>
    );
});

const DialogContent = withStyles((theme) => ({
    root: {
      padding: theme.spacing(2),
    },
  }))(MuiDialogContent);
  
  const DialogActions = withStyles((theme) => ({
    root: {
      margin: 0,
      padding: theme.spacing(1),
    },
  }))(MuiDialogActions);
  

const SelecElo = ({ open=true, handleClose=()=>{}, desired=false, disabledFrom='' }) => {

  return (
    <HeaderProfileContainer>
      <Dialog fullWidth={ true } onClose={handleClose} aria-labelledby="customized-dialog-title" open={open}>
        <DialogTitle id="customized-dialog-title" onClose={handleClose}>
          Selecionar Elo
        </DialogTitle>
        <DialogContent dividers>
        <Box display={{ xs: 'none', s: 'none', md: 'block' }} style={ { width: '100%'} }>
        <Grid container
          direction="row"
          style={ { padding: '8px 0', textAlign: 'center' }}
          justify="center"
          alignItems="center">
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={2}
                style={disabledFrom.includes('bronze') ? { color: 'red' } : {color: 'blue' } }
            >
                FERRO 4
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={2}>
                BRONZE 4
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={2}>
                PRATA 4
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={2}>
                OURO 4
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={2}>
                PLATINA 4
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={2}>
                DIAMANTE 4
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
          <Grid container
          direction="row"
          style={ { padding: '8px 0', textAlign: 'center' }}
          justify="center"
          alignItems="center">
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={2}>
                FERRO 3
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={2}>
                BRONZE 3
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={2}>
                PRATA 3
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={2}>
                OURO 3
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={2}>
                PLATINA 3
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={2}>
                DIAMANTE 3
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
          <Grid container
          direction="row"
          style={ { padding: '8px 0', textAlign: 'center' }}
          justify="center"
          alignItems="center">
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={2}>
                FERRO 2
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={2}>
                BRONZE 2
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={2}>
                PRATA 2
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={2}>
                OURO 2
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={2}>
                PLATINA 2
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={2}>
                DIAMANTE 2
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
          <Grid container
          direction="row"
          style={ { padding: '8px 0', textAlign: 'center' }}
          justify="center"
          alignItems="center">
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={2}>
                FERRO 1
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={2}>
                BRONZE 1
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={2}>
                PRATA 1
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={2}>
                OURO 1
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={2}>
                PLATINA 1
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={2}>
                DIAMANTE 1
            </Grid>
          </Grid>

        </Box>

        <Box display={{ xs: 'block', s: 'block', md: 'none' }} style={ { width: '100%'} }>

        <Grid container
          direction="row"
          style={ { padding: '8px 0', textAlign: 'center' }}
          justify="center"
          alignItems="center">
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={3}>
                FERRO 4
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={3}>
                FERRO 3
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={3}>
                FERRO 2
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={3}>
                FERRO 1
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
          <Grid container
          direction="row"
          style={ { padding: '8px 0', textAlign: 'center' }}
          justify="center"
          alignItems="center">
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={3}>
                BRONZE 4
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={3}>
                BRONZE 3
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={3}>
                BRONZE 2
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={3}>
                BRONZE 1
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
          <Grid container
          direction="row"
          style={ { padding: '8px 0', textAlign: 'center' }}
          justify="center"
          alignItems="center">
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={3}>
                PRATA 4
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={3}>
                PRATA 3
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={3}>
                PRATA 2
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={3}>
                PRATA 1
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
          <Grid container
          direction="row"
          style={ { padding: '8px 0', textAlign: 'center' }}
          justify="center"
          alignItems="center">
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={3}>
                OURO 4
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={3}>
                OURO 3
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={3}>
                OURO 2
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={3}>
                OURO 1
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
          <Grid container
          style={ { padding: '8px 0', textAlign: 'center' }}
          direction="row"
          style={ { padding: '8px 0', textAlign: 'center' }}
          justify="center"
          alignItems="center">
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={3}>
                PLATINA 4
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={3}>
                PLATINA 3
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={3}>
                PLATINA 2
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={3}>
                PLATINA 1
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
          <Grid container
          direction="row"
          style={ { padding: '8px 0', textAlign: 'center' }}
          justify="center"
          alignItems="center">
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={3}>
                DIAMANTE 4
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={3}>
                DIAMANTE 3
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={3}>
                DIAMANTE 2
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} s={12} md={3}>
                DIAMANTE 1
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
          </Box>
        </DialogContent>
        <DialogActions>
          <Button autoFocus onClick={handleClose} color="primary">
            Confirmar
          </Button>
        </DialogActions>
      </Dialog>
    </HeaderProfileContainer>
  );
}

export default SelecElo;
